document_data.caption: A map of the Pirate Isles showing the Fang Rocks in the northwest.
document_data.name: Fang Rocks
document_data.Geography: The Fang Rocks were situated near the halfway point in the waters between [[Kelthann]] and [[Dragonisle]],
document_data.Description: Most of the reef was only visible at low tide, making it particularly dangerous to incoming vessels unaware of the region's geography. They covered an area of sea roughly {{SI|10|mi|long=yes}} in radius.
document_data.History: A fleet of twenty warships from [[Sembia]] was sent to destroy [[Immurk]] and his band of followers in the Pirate Isles in [[1180 DR]]. Unaware of the hidden Fang Rocks, all but three of the warships were destroyed by the reef.
